Matthew Lintz (born May 23, 2001) is an American actor. He comes from a family of actors as his mother, Kelly Lintz, is an actress, along with his brother, Macsen, and his two older sisters, Mackenzie and Madison. He is best known for playing the role of Matty in Pixels.

